♪In this long journey♪

135
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:26,220
♪Love is shining gently♪

136
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:31,100
♪In our eyes♪

137
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:39,700
♪It's my honour♪

